room_title: Escape room "Hang ‘Em High" by Try-N-Escape in Miami
room_address: 3350 NW 2nd Avenue A2 Boca Raton, FL 33431
room_description: You and your posse just pulled off the biggest heist in Texas state history. But there’s only one problem… half your crew got sloppy at the local saloon and were picked up by the local sheriff and thrown in jail. It’s up to you and the rest of your posse to get into the jail and break out your crew before the sheriff gets back in town or… you’ll face the hang man’s noose. Do you think you’re up for the challenge? Good Luck! Try-n-escape!
